{"tid":839932,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救post］我女朋友跪我","createTime":"2018-09-28T09:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T10:03:05.000Z","uid":15760,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"00e2074cfcf2f5f9bc89b443c7da5976c8ff93dc","tid":839932,"uid":15760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T09:53:47.000Z","msg":"頭先行行下街 佢突然間跪低咗仲扯我條褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到好似想幫我含咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n仲要咁啱有個小妹妹經過 個小妹妹問佢啊媽「媽咪 佢地做緊咩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n問完之後佢啊媽就急急腳拖住個女走咗<br />\n其實之前都係咁 成日行行下都會跪低除我條褲 <br />\n都會唔知佢想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n真係睇少一眼就會俾佢除曬條褲含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想問可以點解決依個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日都搞到我係街度扯到行曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f63b6d881e4803da0e8d312467e227d29c313a8","tid":839932,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T09:55:45.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"f9566d57fc490371181942bc6af600f59d538e29","tid":839932,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T09:57:03.000Z","msg":"搶先含左佢先"},{"pid":"c0f6d1ec8a543b25cc989dcfb6c315880aa3848f","tid":839932,"uid":66889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T09:57:17.000Z","msg":"你幫佢含咗先"},{"pid":"6c5cd1dcae828f57d41b2b01c93e728bfba4d149","tid":839932,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T10:00:44.000Z","msg":"樓主係龍心第幾個人格？"},{"pid":"d7e50da16099f5349680fa353f8585b474c9a84f","tid":839932,"uid":86692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T10:03:05.000Z","msg":"零分重作"}]}